Comment: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:58.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}崩れて終わる世界
Comment: 0,0:00:58.49,0:01:07.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}無慈悲に告げる
Comment: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:14.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}君は  一人
Comment: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:20.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}何を  聞いてた
Comment: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:26.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}僕は  遠い
Comment: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:33.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}夢を  見てた
Comment: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:35.24,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}何を選び取る
Comment: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:36.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}何を諦める
Comment: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:38.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}決めようとしてる
Comment: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:40.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}僕は何様だ
Comment: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:41.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}何を選ぶかは
Comment: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:43.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}もう決まっている
Comment: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:44.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}間違いは無いか
Comment: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:46.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}神に問いかける
Comment: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:49.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}一人きりじゃなかった
Comment: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:51.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}ずっとそばにいたんだ
Comment: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:58.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}この手を伸ばす
Comment: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:01.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}怖いものなんかない
Comment: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:05.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}たとえ化け物になろうとも
Comment: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:13.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}成し遂げる
Comment: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:58.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}崩壞的終焉之世
Comment: 0,0:00:58.49,0:01:07.46,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}無情告知
Comment: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:14.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}你默默一人
Comment: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:20.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}在聆聽什麼
Comment: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:26.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}而我恍惚
Comment: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:33.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}如在遠夢中彷徨
Comment: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:35.24,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}選擇什麼
Comment: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:36.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}放棄什麼
Comment: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:38.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}我有何權力
Comment: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:40.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}做這些決定
Comment: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:41.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}如何選擇
Comment: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:43.29,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}已經確定
Comment: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:44.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}有否錯誤
Comment: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:46.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}向神詢問
Comment: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:49.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}你不是一個人
Comment: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:51.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}一直在你身邊
Comment: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:58.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}將這雙手伸出
Comment: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:01.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}無所畏懼
Comment: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:05.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}就算是化身怪物
Comment: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:13.69,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}定將完成夙願
